1. create  %appdata%/Local/nvim folder
mkdir %appdata%/Local/nvim OR C:\Users\<userName>\AppData\Local\nvim

2. create init.lua file in that directory

Plugins
3. execute powershell script from github.com/junegunn/vim-plug in Neovim section

4. Install C++ dependencies for LSPs (Windows): 
    - Set-ExecutionPolicy Bypass -Scope Process -Force; [System.Net.ServicePointManager]::SecurityProtocol = [System.Net.ServicePointManager]::SecurityProtocol -bor 3072; iex ((New-Object System.Net.WebClient).DownloadString('https://community.chocolatey.org/install.ps1'))
    - choco install zig
